I"<h2 id="raspbian下安装软件命令">raspbian下安装软件命令</h2>

<div class="language-shell highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="nb">sudo </span>apt-get <span class="nb">install </span>xxxxxx
</code></pre></div></div>

<h2 id="软件源更改">软件源更改</h2>

<div class="language-shell highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="nb">sudo cp</span> /etc/apt/sources.list  /etc/apt/sources.list_backup 

<span class="nb">sudo </span>nano /etc/apt/sources.list 

把官方网址改成国内源的网址，例如：
http://mirrors.aliyun.com/raspbian/raspbian/

<span class="nb">sudo </span>apt-get update
</code></pre></div></div>

<h2 id="安装中文输入法">安装中文输入法</h2>
<div class="language-shell highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="nb">sudo </span>apt-get <span class="nb">install </span>fcitx fcitx-googlepinyin fcitx-module-cloudpinyin fcitx-sunpinyin 
</code></pre></div></div>

